OL,3,CThree men deny charges in connection
OL,4,Cwith alleged sex abuse of woman by
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FThree men have denied offences in
OL,8,Fconnection with the alleged drugging
OL,9,Fand sexual abuse of a woman by her
OL,10,Fhusband.
OL,12,FThe husband, who cannot be identified
OL,13,Ffor legal reasons, is also said to
OL,14,Fhave conspired with others to commit
OL,15,Fsexual offences against her while she
OL,16,Fwas unconscious.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
