CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774094596
OL,3,CThree men deny charges in connection
OL,4,Cwith alleged sex abuse of woman by
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FIn February, the man aged in his 60s
OL,8,Ffrom Greater Manchester denied a total
OL,9,Fof 48 allegations spanning a 20-year
OL,10,Fperiod ` including rape, conspiracy to
OL,11,Frape and and administering a substance
OL,12,Fwith intent to stupefy or overpower.
OL,14,FOn Friday 20 March, three of his co-
OL,15,Fdefendants, who also cannot be named,
OL,16,Fentered pleas at Manchester Minshull
OL,17,FStreet Crown Court to the charges they
OL,18,Ffaced.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
