PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774094596
OL,3,CThree men deny charges in connection
OL,4,Cwith alleged sex abuse of woman by
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FA man in his 50s pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Fconspiracy to rape, conspiracy to
OL,9,Fcommit assault by penetration and
OL,10,Fconspiracy to administer a substance
OL,11,Fwith intent to stupefy or overpower.
OL,13,FA man in his 40s denied rape,
OL,14,Fconspiracy to rape and conspiracy to
OL,15,Fcommit assault by penetration.
OL,17,FA man in his 50s pleaded not guilty to
OL,18,Fassault by penetration, sexual assault
OL,19,Fand conspiracy to commit assault by
OL,20,Fpenetration.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
