PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774094596
OL,3,CThree men deny charges in connection
OL,4,Cwith alleged sex abuse of woman by
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FIn February, six other co-defendants
OL,8,Falso denied similar offences, while
OL,9,Fone man in his 50s from Scotland
OL,10,Fpleaded guilty to assault by
OL,11,Fpenetration, conspiracy to rape,
OL,12,Fconspiracy to commit assault by
OL,13,Fpenetration and conspiracy to
OL,14,Fadminister a substance with intent to
OL,15,Fstupefy or overpower.
OL,17,FTwo of the 13 men charged in the
OL,18,Finvestigation have yet to enter pleas.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
